Package: survTrial
Title: PFS trial simulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Reeves",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "john.reeves.ext@bayer.com")
Description: Simulated PFS times for Sip-T project.  Progression and death events are genereated
    for 2 treatment groups.  Options include moving progression events forward to next
    scheduled visit, and censored times back to most recent visit.  Data cut-off is specified
    for the nth event.
